                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5871" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0544</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7522 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">卓越模式下的停滞：亿瓦新能源创业路上的股权困局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Stasis in the model of excellence: Equity dilemma on the road to EWA’s new energy entrepreneurship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李振华，杨旭楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京亿瓦能源科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">亿瓦；“云管端”模式；初创企业；股权结构；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EWA; Cloud management mode; Startups; Equity structure；Corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了北京亿瓦能源科技有限公司采用“云管端”商业模式，将“互联网+预约充电”平台成功应用于新能源汽车充电运营领域，却因创业初期股权结构及公司治理结构设置不合理陷入困局的创业历程。针对“有车无处充电、有桩无人问津”的行业痛点，亿瓦创新性地探索“预约充电、分时共享”的充电模式，旨在为客户提供更加优质的服务。然而，创业初期1:1的股权结构、经营权与财务权分离引发的控制权缺失，阻碍了亿瓦前进的步伐，令亿瓦业务被迫停滞，运营陷入僵局。通过案例分析，旨在帮助学员了解新能源汽车充电运营企业的创业发展之路，理解“云管端”商业模式、目标用户确定及初创企业股权比例和治理结构设置对后期发展的重要意义，为其他中小型初创企业提供借鉴与指导。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The Beijing internet energy technology company EWA successfully applied the Internet plus reservation charging platform to the new energy vehicle charging and operation field. However, it failed because of the irrational equity and governance structure at the beginning of the business. In view of the industry pain point of &quot;there is no place to charge the car, there is no one to pay attention to the pile&quot;, EWA innovatively explores the charging mode of &quot;appointment charging, time sharing&quot;, aiming to provide more quality service for customers. However, the contradiction between the 1:1 ownership structure and the lack of control caused by the separation of management rights and financial rights in the early stage of the venture hindered the progress of EWA，forcing EWA &#39;s business to stall and operation into an impasse . Through the case analysis, it aims to help students understand the entrepreneurial development path of new energy vehicle charging operation enterprises, understand the significance of &quot;cloud management end&quot; business model, target user determination, start-up equity ratio setting and governance structure setting for later development, thus providing reference and guidance for other small and medium-sized start-up enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业与创新管理》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部创业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
